1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,725
Let’s finish your work.

2
00:00:01,720 --> 00:00:03,748
I know you’ve always wanted to do it.

3
00:00:03,740 --> 00:00:04,971
Hello, Mr. Montree.

4
00:00:04,970 --> 00:00:07,451
I finally get to meet you, Mr. Art.

5
00:00:07,851 --> 00:00:10,240
- What did you do to Kao? What did you do?
- Stop.

6
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,691
You didn’t mean it.

7
00:00:13,428 --> 00:00:16,034
I didn’t do it.

8
00:00:16,030 --> 00:00:17,177
He’s not the culprit.

9
00:00:17,170 --> 00:00:18,034
Found the bloodstain.

10
00:00:18,148 --> 00:00:19,908
Can we release Art?

11
00:00:19,908 --> 00:00:23,020
He has nothing to do with Kao’s disappearance.

12
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:24,411
No use to keep being persistent.

13
00:00:24,410 --> 00:00:26,537
Better let them live together happily. Don’t get in the way.

14
00:00:26,537 --> 00:00:29,580
But if I really love someone, I’m willing to waste my time, Phaya.

15
00:00:29,714 --> 00:00:32,500
Tharn, I’m going to do everything to have you by my side.

16
00:01:51,417 --> 00:01:52,605
Please stop.

17
00:01:52,902 --> 00:01:57,680
If you keep doing this, your soul will be destroyed one day.

18
00:01:58,342 --> 00:02:00,194
He messes with what is mine.

19
00:02:00,754 --> 00:02:01,942
He has to die!

20
00:02:03,337 --> 00:02:07,382
Nothing ever belongs to you, you are well aware of that.

21
00:02:07,380 --> 00:02:08,994
Tharn didn’t choose you.

22
00:02:09,908 --> 00:02:15,020
The worst sin in life is to think only about oneself.

23
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:20,354
This love full of selfishness that you’re trying hold on to...

24
00:02:20,845 --> 00:02:24,800
will eventually burn you to hell.

25
00:02:25,531 --> 00:02:26,640
I don’t care.

26
00:02:27,554 --> 00:02:29,760
I will never let them be together.

27
00:02:30,890 --> 00:02:35,337
Tharn has to be with me, and I will make them parted for eternity.

28
00:03:01,490 --> 00:03:03,268
Tharn, wake up.

29
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,245
Tharn.

30
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,577
Wake up.

31
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,340
Phaya!

32
00:03:17,782 --> 00:03:18,605
Hey!

33
00:03:26,708 --> 00:03:27,771
What happened?

34
00:03:28,845 --> 00:03:30,331
Are you okay?

35
00:03:36,091 --> 00:03:36,971
Yeah.

36
00:03:39,862 --> 00:03:41,851
Did you have a bad dream again?

37
00:03:49,794 --> 00:03:50,628
Yeah.

38
00:03:53,634 --> 00:03:59,577
In that dream, someone was trying to strangle me.

39
00:04:02,262 --> 00:04:03,805
It was so real.

40
00:04:28,937 --> 00:04:30,822
I think you should wear this necklace while you sleep.

41
00:04:38,777 --> 00:04:39,588
Okay.

42
